calculatedFields.name: last_used_date_6_months
calculatedFields.expression:
/*
(AI generated) select all the dates apart from last 6 months
*/
ifelse(dateDiff({flexera_installation_last_used_date}, addDateTime(-6, 'MM', now())) >= 0, {flexera_installation_last_used_date}, NULL)

calculatedFields.name: openit_monthly_summary_month_parsed
calculatedFields.expression:
/*
(AI generated) if there is null value then a date with year 1999 parseDate({openit_monthly_summary_month}, 'yyyy-MM-dd')
*/

/*
(AI generated) if value is not convertable to date then put date from 1999
*/
ifelse(isNotNull(parseDate({openit_monthly_summary_month}, 'yyyy-MM-dd')), parseDate({openit_monthly_summary_month}, 'yyyy-MM-dd'), parseDate('1999-01-01', 'yyyy-MM-dd'))
